name: Cooper Bussmann 3A Automotive Fuses (5-Pack)
description: The Cooper Bussmann AGC Series 3 Amp Silver Automotive Fuses (5-Pack) are intended for use in automotive applications. These fuses are rated for up to 3 amps and 250 volts each.
